  "identifier": "HB 739",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to the partial distribution of pari-mutuel racing tax receipts to local governments.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 138.510 to allocate moneys from the pari-mutuel racing excise tax distribution to the local government support fund; create a new section of KRS Chapter 230 to establish the pari-mutuel racing local government support fund to be administered by the Department for Local Government; establish parameters for use of fund moneys; amend KRS 131.190 to allow the Department of Revenue to share information relating to the calculation of the new fund distribution.",
